descript.abstract:
***This dataset has been superseded by Municipal Boundaries (1997).*** It is intended for use with older legacy datasets that are still available from RIGIS. Data includes municipality name, unique ID, city and town name annotation coded attributes.
These data were originally published by RIGIS in 1989.
descript.purpose: The dataset represents state, county, city, and town political boundaries for Rhode Island.

procstep.procdesc: State coast and municipal boundaries manually digitized from the most recent available USGS mylar 7-5 minute quad maps.

Renamed dataset from "Municipalities" to "Municipal Boundaries (1989); muni89." Re-titled RIGIS shapefile download from "towns" to "muni89." Updated metadata title, abstract, suggested citation, access and use constraints, spatial reference information, distribution information, and metadata information. Deleted redundant attribute overview description.
